{
  "id": "61e91b38b3495c001e9ef8b5",
  "title": "Call for Reviewers",
  "created": 1553773903,
  "updated": 1626850488,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad45",
      "text": "Call for Reviewers",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad46",
      "text": "\tYou can see the contents of the book here: [/intellitech-en]",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad47",
      "text": "\t\tYou are required to be interested in the content of this book.",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad48",
      "text": "\t\t\tIf you are not interested in the book, applying this review is not good for both you and me.",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad49",
      "text": "\t\tI can give you PDF, ePub or Mobi files if you want.",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad4a",
      "text": "\t\t\tI use LeanPub for file distribution: https://leanpub.com/intellitech-howtoboostyourcreativity",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad4b",
      "text": "\t\t\tI can give you a coupon to get the book free of charge.",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad4c",
      "text": "\tIf you have experiences of programming, it is better, but it is not required.",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad4d",
      "text": "\tEven if you are not native English speaker, it does not matter. I want to express in simple English that everyone can understand even they are not native.",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1626848667,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad4e",
      "text": "\tIf you want you can put your name on the `Acknowledgments` section and it go along with further translation from English.",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1626848677,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad4f",
      "text": " I'm not sure the best way to manage this project. Let me hear your opinion.",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad50",
      "text": "  My suggestion: start with one-hour trial, then discuss ",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad51",
      "text": "  I want to hear anything you think, especially which section is difficult to understand. ",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad52",
      "text": "\t\tIt is difficult to define required quality of review comments, so feel easy. I hope you enjoy reading my book.",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad53",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553773903,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad54",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1553773916,
      "updated": 1553773916,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad55",
      "text": "What kind of review I need:",
      "created": 1553773917,
      "updated": 1626849654,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad56",
      "text": "\tI am trying to make the text understandable for people all over the world.",
      "created": 1626849655,
      "updated": 1626849682,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad57",
      "text": " \tSo I would like to know any questions or [IWAKAN] (a sense of disharmony) that came to your mind while you were reading the text.",
      "created": 1626849682,
      "updated": 1626850488,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad58",
      "text": "\t\tThe information about sections you feel difficult, confusing or questionable is valuable.",
      "created": 1626849700,
      "updated": 1626849919,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad59",
      "text": "\t\tI appreciate any comments and questions. Questions can help me to describe more precisely.",
      "created": 1626849919,
      "updated": 1626849919,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad5a",
      "text": "\tThere is no need to admire this book. Your review is not for displaying in bookstore. It is for improving my manuscript.",
      "created": 1553774175,
      "updated": 1626849915,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad5b",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1553774070,
      "updated": 1626849918,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad5c",
      "text": "How to feedback:",
      "created": 1626849971,
      "updated": 1626849988,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad5d",
      "text": "\tFeel easy to send me an email: nishio 'dot' hirokazu 'at' gmail 'dot' com",
      "created": 1626849988,
      "updated": 1626850045,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad5e",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1626849996,
      "updated": 1626850055,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad5f",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1626849592,
      "updated": 1626850059,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad60",
      "text": "\tIf you read PDF in the Preview app in Mac, you can use `Cmd+[` to back link.",
      "created": 1553773903,
      "updated": 1553774263,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad61",
      "text": "\tIt is okay to use PDF annotation to respond comments to me.",
      "created": 1553774263,
      "updated": 1553774293,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad62",
      "text": "\t\tTell me if you have better way to do this task.",
      "created": 1553774297,
      "updated": 1553774331,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad63",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1554197170,
      "updated": 1626849611,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad64",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1554197172,
      "updated": 1554197172,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad65",
      "text": "I think there are 3 kinds of issues:",
      "created": 1556693956,
      "updated": 1556694039,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad66",
      "text": "\tSemantic issues: you find it difficult to understand.",
      "created": 1556693962,
      "updated": 1556694051,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad67",
      "text": "\tGrammatical issues: you understand the meaning but the syntax is not correct.",
      "created": 1556694052,
      "updated": 1556694095,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad68",
      "text": "\tStyle issues: you understand the meaning and the syntax is correct, but you think it is not a natural expression.",
      "created": 1556694095,
      "updated": 1556694193,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad69",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1556694187,
      "updated": 1556694187,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad6a",
      "text": "Currently I focused on the semantic issues.",
      "created": 1556694187,
      "updated": 1626850089,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad6b",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1556693951,
      "updated": 1626850088,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad6c",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1558499957,
      "updated": 1558499957,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000d0ad6d",
      "text": "[en.icon]",
      "created": 1626850488,
      "updated": 1626850488,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    }
  ]
}